Class FlinkPartialReduceFunction<K,InputT,AccumT,W extends BoundedWindow>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlinkMergingPartialReduceFunction

    public class FlinkPartialReduceFunction<K,InputT,AccumT,W extends BoundedWindow>
extends org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.RichGroupCombineFunction<WindowedValue<KV<K,InputT>>,WindowedValue<KV<K,AccumT>>>
    This is is the first step for executing a Combine.PerKey on Flink. The second part is FlinkReduceFunction. This function performs a local combine step before shuffling while the latter does the final combination after a shuffle.

    The input to combine(Iterable, Collector) are elements of the same key but for different windows. We have to ensure that we only combine elements of matching windows.
